data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!! Rural and Rare find in the heart of Pace with a POOL! This beautiful white farmhouse sits on 1 acre of land. Recent upgrades include a metal roof, flooring, AC unit and water heater!! This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a bonus room/office or upstairs loft space. You decide! The loft is quite large and overlooks the dining area and huge backyard. Kitchen appliances have been updated to stainless steel with a custom stove. The spacious dining room has a ceiling that stretches to the 2nd story giving great light. A custom wood counter and open wall allows for a pass through from the kitchen. The Master bedroom is located just off the living area and has a newly remodeled bathroom that has a double vanity sink and a walk-in closet. The additional two bedrooms arenicely sized with ample closet space. Out the back door you will find a great place to relax on the oversized screen porch. The exterior features a Beautiful Heated and Chilled Saltwater, Screened In Pool! Detached garage/workshop complete with electrical. This home also has an EV or RV charger and water softener.
